# This pseudocode finds the largest of three numbers.
# It takes three numbers as input and outputs
# the largest of the three numbers.
# by comparing each number with the others.
INPUT num1
INPUT num2
INPUT num3
IF num1 > num2 AND num1 > num3 THEN
    OUTPUT "The largest number is: " + num1
ELSE IF num2 > num1 AND num2 > num3 THEN
    OUTPUT "The largest number is: " + num2
ELSE
    OUTPUT "The largest number is: " + num3
ENDIF